  "remarks": "Concern Radio-Electronic Technologies KRET is Russia’s major developer and manufacturer of military radio-electronic products. It is a Rostec subsidiary. It manufactured Krasukha-4 electronic warfare systems, that were used by the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation during Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine.",
